message.body: Hi Cashew! How are you feeling on this fine, wet Thursday?
Feels like it should be Friday already!
Tell me about it! My twins decided this week that they don't like sleeping anymore.
Ugh! That's not good. Do you think it is the change in weather?
It's possible. Any time there's a change in infant behavior, there's always about 1000 potentially valid hypotheses for the cause.
Yeah and with twins they prolly affect each other so much too ... If ones in a foul mood, the other will be too
Have you taken them on many outings yet? Do they like the car rides?
